reviewText: Not as described. Was not the COLLECTOR'S SET!! Ended up with 3 DVD'S that had all episodes that should have been on 1 DVD. They don't play in Blue ray players. They play in reg. dvd player, but not very well. Seam to be copies!!! Buyers beware.

First off La Blue Girl is one of my favorite titles but the seller on here is giving bootlegs and when I actually opened the dvd that was supposedly brand new it had chunks ... YES chunks of the dvd taken out on the disk and was scratched up horribly.... I went to ebay and got a real box set!
Me and my penis thank you, I mean my root of lust!
if this is the kinda of stuff you're looking for then you're in luck.
